{"tid":1327491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「我係和理非/勇武派」，試着說「因週邊情況，我需要做前線/哨兵/物資傳遞/採購/跑手/車手/叫囂侮辱/吶喊助威」","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:19:04.000Z","uid":131691,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7098f99b0133dfd5031db4557722edde3eb8af8d","tid":1327491,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"Be water!<br />\n唔好畀自己set死個工作崗位<br />\n每個香港人，喺唔同嘅時間，唔同嘅環境，都可以極速應變<br />\n呢個就係香港人嘅本性<br />\n<br />\n見到前線唔夠人嘅，平時做慣物資人鏈嘅不妨去第4/5排以後幫手，做個前線嘅後援<br />\n前線前排真係需要休息，不妨脫離陣線，周圍做下哨兵，或者去物資鏈傳一陣<br />\n唔夠物資嘅時候，自己又有經濟能力，不妨自己，甚至拉隔離幾個香港人一齊去採購<br />\n<br />\n唔好喺人羣之中set死自己嘅崗位<br />\nBe water"},{"pid":"a04669b1fca98e7d7cd21a5c83c725a5d77c5e71","tid":1327491,"uid":131691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cJMwBwFj5nQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcJMwBwFj5nQ&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=0707ef09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cJMwBwFj5nQ</a>"},{"pid":"afef2443f76d2776d14e2db47a871dd5fb866c64","tid":1327491,"uid":35842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"[721見] 如何正確隱藏身份 (整合+進階篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327279</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9Pobuw7Wk2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Pobuw7Wk2k&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=2a947d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9Pobuw7Wk2k</a> <br />\n唔想專登買面罩其實用Tee都得<br />\n<br />\n✅ DNS用1.1.1.1（尤其係3HK、HKT用戶）<br />\n✅ 上討論區用Tor Browser，但唔好用Tor Browser Login 任何帳號<br />\n✅ P2P通訊用Telegram / Signal<br />\n✅ Group通訊用Signal<br />\n✅ 即時戰略遊戲用Playstation Message傾<br />\n✅ 電話唔好用指紋/面容解鎖<br />\n✅ 重要嘢面談<br />\n✅ 食煙嘅你買個打火機同包純薄萬傍身<br />\n✅ 飲酒嘅你飲樽裝好飲過罐裝<br />\n✅ 有時毒撚一個更開心，唔洗吓吓同人一齊玩<br />\n✅ 毒撚自己一個玩，唔好去多狗地方玩<br />\n<br />\n❌ 咪撚帶八達通同信用卡<br />\n❌ 咪撚著拖鞋短褲同容易辨認嘅衣物<br />\n❌ 咪撚咁傻仔帶啲唔合理嘅物品係身，例如拍戲道具<br />\n❌ 咪撚除/拉低口罩<br />\n❌ 咪撚影人樣，影狗同影景就夠<br />\n<br />\n❗關閉電話上所有Facebook、WhatsApp同Instagram權限<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1629975780370609/posts/2528022960565882?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1629975780370609%2Fposts%2F2528022960565882%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=dd9d604b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1629975780370609/posts/2528022960565882?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://github.com/cybersec-hk/digital_awareness_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fcybersec-hk%2Fdigital_awareness_hk&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=f04ca96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">github.com/cybersec-hk/digital_awareness_hk</a>"},{"pid":"3d0d8b70394afbeed63200f974e6b5be07c5c2f7","tid":1327491,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04669b1fca98e7d7cd21a5c83c725a5d77c5e71","tid":1327491,"uid":131691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cJMwBwFj5nQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcJMwBwFj5nQ&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=0707ef09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cJMwBwFj5nQ</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91cd3caa7af17ed6d963e9769d0210b1c78e5a0","tid":1327491,"uid":256914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"我需要做 班警犬世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla